Zlatan Ibrahimovic had his four-game ban reduced to three after appealing to the French Olympic Committee . 
  Dimitri Payet has also had his ban reduced by one match . 
  Ibrahimovic was caught on camera abusing Ligue 1 referees after PSG's loss to Bordeaux . 
  The striker will now miss three games and Payet just one . 
  PSG and Marseille successfully appealed the bans . 
 